<docbook><section><title>VirtTipsAndTricksGuideRunAs</title><bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2">How can I specify OS user name to which the Virtuoso server will switch after opening the listen ports?</bridgehead>
<para>You can specify the OS user name to which the Virtuoso server will switch after opening the listen ports, by setting the <emphasis><ulink url="RunAs">RunAs</ulink></emphasis> parameter in the Virtuoso ini file, in the  <emphasis>Parameters</emphasis> section.</para>
